WEBVTT

1
00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:06.000
PLANET: HOLZHERR
SOLAR CATEGORY: RED

2
00:15:48.000 --> 00:15:50.000
We will take Elias's daughter?

3
00:15:51.000 --> 00:15:53.000
The cells are completely full. right?

4
00:15:57.000 --> 00:15:59.500
What do you think about my new ship?

5
00:19:52.000 --> 00:19:54.000
Who are you?

6
00:22:12.500 --> 00:22:15.000
What did you hit this time. Lloyd?

7
00:23:19.000 --> 00:23:20.000
The watch

8
00:27:59.500 --> 00:28:00.800
She's heading for the sun.

9
00:29:05.000 --> 00:29:06.500
We lost the engines!

10
00:29:08.000 --> 00:29:09.300
There they are

11
00:29:33.000 --> 00:29:37.000
INTERPLANETARY STATION
SOLAR CATEGORY: YELLOW

12
00:31:16.000 --> 00:31:16.500
Tell her

13
00:31:16.600 --> 00:31:18.000
Krem has the strength of a thousand men

14
00:31:18.200 --> 00:31:21.000
He will tear her to pieces.

15
00:32:47.000 --> 00:32:49.700
PLANET: BILEUS
SOLAR CATEGORY: YELLOW

16
00:34:19.500 --> 00:34:21.500
Excuse me. it's very crowded.

17
00:38:37.500 --> 00:38:38.300
Have you guys seen him?

18
00:42:48.500 --> 00:42:50.500
Is it now? I thought we had more time.

19
00:42:50.600 --> 00:42:54.000
Me too. but Krypton's core is highly unstable.

20
00:42:54.500 --> 00:42:56.000
It will explode in minutes.

21
00:42:57.000 --> 00:43:00.000
Activate the force field.
We must leave.

22
00:43:01.000 --> 00:43:01.600
Alura!

23
00:43:02.000 --> 00:43:03.000
Now!

24
00:43:12.000 --> 00:43:13.000
Is it him?

25
00:43:15.000 --> 00:43:16.500
It's Kal-El.

26
00:43:17.000 --> 00:43:20.000
Your brother declared him
conqueror of worlds.

27
00:43:24.000 --> 00:43:26.000
The time has come.

28
00:44:17.000 --> 00:44:19.500
Were we foolish. Zor-El?

29
00:44:20.000 --> 00:44:23.500
Should we have listened to your brother?

30
00:44:24.000 --> 00:44:26.700
We cannot send our daughter...

31
00:44:27.000 --> 00:44:28.700
...to another planet to be some kind of god.

32
00:44:29.000 --> 00:44:31.000
We preserved this for a reason.

33
00:44:33.000 --> 00:44:37.000
We have to believe there is a future here.

34
00:44:44.000 --> 00:44:46.000
Kara. where are you?

35
00:45:20.000 --> 00:45:21.000
Tell me.

36
00:45:22.700 --> 00:45:24.700
When Argo City broke away...

37
00:45:25.000 --> 00:45:30.000
..it unearthed a crystalline mineral
from the depths of the planet.

38
00:45:31.000 --> 00:45:32.000
Kryptonite.

39
00:45:33.000 --> 00:45:35.700
The soil is poisoned.

40
00:45:36.000 --> 00:45:38.400
It made all the people of Argo sick...

41
00:45:38.700 --> 00:45:38.700
..and it is spreading.

42
00:45:43.000 --> 00:45:46.000
Is there anything we can do?

43
00:46:05.000 --> 00:46:06.500
What's that?

44
00:46:09.000 --> 00:46:10.800
It’s what I have been working on.

45
00:46:11.000 --> 00:46:14.000
I don’t have an antidote for any of us.

46
00:46:17.000 --> 00:46:19.000
The radiation has taken hold of me too.

47
00:46:20.000 --> 00:46:21.500
I won't let it reach you.

48
00:46:25.000 --> 00:46:28.000
I found my brother's plans
for the escape pod.

49
00:46:29.000 --> 00:46:31.000
I built one for you.

50
00:46:32.000 --> 00:46:35.000
You will follow your cousin. Kal-El.

51
00:46:36.500 --> 00:46:40.000
You will have a new home on Earth.

52
00:46:43.000 --> 00:46:43.500
No!

53
00:46:45.000 --> 00:46:46.000
This is my home.

54
00:46:47.000 --> 00:46:50.500
It's my only home.

55
00:46:53.000 --> 00:46:56.000
Let the radiation reach me.

56
00:46:57.000 --> 00:47:00.500
I will lie on the ground next to you and Ma.

57
00:47:04.000 --> 00:47:06.000
I am only one small life.

58
00:47:07.000 --> 00:47:10.700
What difference does it make if I live or die?

59
00:47:11.000 --> 00:47:14.000
You are not just one small life.

60
00:47:15.000 --> 00:47:18.000
You are your mother's life.

61
00:47:20.000 --> 00:47:21.500
You are my life.

62
00:47:23.000 --> 00:47:26.000
You are our souls
unfolding into the future.

63
00:47:27.500 --> 00:47:29.000
My daughter...

64
00:47:29.300 --> 00:47:32.000
...this is the reason for your existence.

65
00:47:45.000 --> 00:47:47.000
When I am gone...

66
00:47:48.000 --> 00:47:52.000
...promise me something.

67
00:47:53.000 --> 00:47:54.500
Of course. Mother.

68
00:47:56.000 --> 00:47:57.700
Be good.

69
00:47:58.000 --> 00:48:01.500
That doesn't mean being weak.

70
00:48:02.000 --> 00:48:06.000
Nor does it mean being nice.

71
00:48:08.000 --> 00:48:10.000
But you must be good.

72
00:48:19.000 --> 00:48:22.000
We do not choose our path.

73
00:48:24.000 --> 00:48:26.000
Your path will be one of great struggle...

74
00:48:29.000 --> 00:48:31.000
...and of great purpose.

75
00:48:33.000 --> 00:48:38.000
Wherever you are going. you will have great power.

76
00:48:39.500 --> 00:48:41.100
Use it to protect those...

77
00:48:41.300 --> 00:48:44.000
...who cannot protect themselves.

78
00:48:45.000 --> 00:48:47.000
Trust in yourself...

79
00:48:47.800 --> 00:48:49.300
...to know what is right.

80
00:49:31.000 --> 00:49:32.700
We are with you.

81
00:52:46.000 --> 00:52:49.000
Bomar. stop! She is our daughter.
we have no choice.

82
00:56:33.000 --> 00:56:34.700
Bring me the girl.

83
00:56:35.000 --> 00:56:36.000
Now.

84
00:57:09.500 --> 00:57:10.700
The girls!

85
00:57:11.000 --> 00:57:12.500
Get them!

86
00:58:29.000 --> 00:58:31.000
A deal is a deal.

87
00:58:31.700 --> 00:58:33.200
She must die.

88
01:06:32.000 --> 01:06:35.000
PLANET: BARENTON
SOLAR CATEGORY: GREEN AND YELLOW

89
01:07:09.000 --> 01:07:11.000
I don't understand what you are saying

90
01:07:11.500 --> 01:07:12.800
Where am I?

91
01:07:13.000 --> 01:07:15.000
Am I on Earth?

92
01:07:16.500 --> 01:07:18.000
Are you Kal-El?

93
01:07:31.000 --> 01:07:33.000
Krypto. behave yourself.

94
01:07:33.700 --> 01:07:34.500
Be good.

95
01:08:35.000 --> 01:08:38.000
Why is he in his underwear?

96
01:09:00.000 --> 01:09:02.500
How can this be my home?

97
01:15:34.000 --> 01:15:36.700
A dead Kryptonian...

98
01:15:37.000 --> 01:15:40.500
...is a magnificent trophy.

99
01:15:41.000 --> 01:15:43.000
I'm handling it.

100
01:18:09.000 --> 01:18:10.500
Move your fat ass...

101
01:18:10.700 --> 01:18:12.300
...and take her to Krem.

102
01:18:12.500 --> 01:18:13.500
He will shut her up.

103
01:18:33.000 --> 01:18:35.000
Shut up and do what you're told.

104
01:21:21.000 --> 01:21:23.700
Where you are going. you will have great power.

105
01:21:24.000 --> 01:21:25.700
I need you to promise me something.

106
01:21:28.000 --> 01:21:29.700
Use it to protect those...

107
01:21:30.000 --> 01:21:32.000
...who cannot protect themselves.
